The evidence with the title 'Social security silliness - factcheck.org ' says Sep 12, 2011  ... The web video correctly says that Perry called Social Security a " failure " and a " Ponzi scheme."As we wrote after the sept. 7 debate, Perry called Social Security a " failure " in his book " FedUp!"(page 62) and a "Ponzi scheme" in the debate. But the ad is wrong to say Romney supports " privatization .".
